OL,3,CHow can I keep my home cool in the
OL,4,Cheat?
OL,6,FAs the weather gets hotter more people
OL,7,Fare looking for ways to stay cool in
OL,8,Fthe heat.
OL,10,FIt comes as an amber heat alert has
OL,11,Fbeen issued for much of the Midlands
OL,12,Fby the UK Health Security Agency.
OL,14,FThe warning will be place across the
OL,15,Fweekend from midday on Friday 1 1 July
OL,16,Funtil 9am on Monday 14 July.
OL,18,FThis is the third heatwave of the
OL,19,Fyear, after amber alerts were also
OL,20,Fissued during consecutive weeks at the
OL,21,Fend of June.
