OL,3,CHow can I keep my home cool in the
OL,4,Cheat?
OL,6,FThe alert means there is potential for
OL,7,Fa rise in deaths, particularly among
OL,8,Fthose aged 65 and over, or with health
OL,9,Fconditions, due to the heat.
OL,11,FSome key ways you can make your homes
OL,12,Fmore comfortable in the cooler
OL,13,Ftemperatures are:
OL,15,FOne way in the future that people can
OL,16,Fkeep themselves cool is through the
OL,17,Fuse of external shading devices which
OL,18,Fexperts are experimenting with at
OL,19,FLoughborough University.
