OL,3,CHow can I keep my home cool in the
OL,4,Cheat?
OL,6,FThe rooms with the shading devices
OL,7,Fwere found to be up 5 degrees cooler
OL,8,Fthan those without them.
OL,10,FDr Ben Roberts, Senior Lecturer in
OL,11,FHealthy Buildings at Loughborough
OL,12,FUniversity and Niloo-Todeh Kharman, a
OL,13,FPHD student are working on the project.
OL,15,FBen said: "They are zero cost to run,
OL,16,Fthey are zero emission to run, you
OL,17,Fhave that one free running cost for
OL,18,Fthe lifetime of the external shading
OL,19,Fdevice.
