OL,3,CHow can I keep my home cool in the
OL,4,Cheat?
OL,6,F"Climate change is continuing, we are
OL,7,Fonly going to see more long hot
OL,8,Fsummers in the UK and this isn't a
OL,9,Fproblem that we can ignore.
OL,11,F"It's really important that we design
OL,12,Four homes to reduce the indoor
OL,13,Ftemperatures and keep people safe and
OL,14,Fhealthy."
OL,16,FThe team are using two side by side
OL,17,Fhomes for the project, which hopes to
OL,18,Fimprove energy efficiency, and they
OL,19,Fsay their findings could reduce indoor
OL,20,Ftemperatures and lead to health
OL,21,Fbenefits for householders.
